data.description: Come check out the charm this well maintained home offers! You are welcomed by a huge covered front porch. The large rooms and high ceilings throughout give a wonderful homey feel. All new cabinets were just installed in the kitchen. Off the kitchen is a huge dining area, that could double as a sun room with several floor to ceiling windows. Off the back of the house is a large deck overlooking the enormous fenced in backyard. The property is 0.85 acres and most of that is behind the home. There is plenty of room for a garden, play-sets, or anything to entertain the entire family! A new roof was added within the last year! Located on a quiet street in downtown Meansville you are just minutes away from Pike County Schools and the Zebulon square. Fiber Internet is currently in the process of being installed! With three over-sized bedrooms and two full baths this is a wonderful opportunity to buy a beautiful home in desirable Pike County under $300k.
